query:
DELETE FROM clientes 
WHERE id IN (
  SELECT id FROM (
    SELECT c1.id
    FROM clientes c1
    INNER JOIN (
      SELECT cnpj, MAX(id) as max_id
      FROM clientes
      WHERE cnpj IS NOT NULL AND cnpj != ''
      GROUP BY cnpj
      HAVING COUNT(*) > 1
    ) c2 ON c1.cnpj = c2.cnpj
    WHERE c1.id < c2.max_id
  ) AS temp
);
